#rstats 
HB <- function(p, alpha = 0.05){
  s <- sort(p)
  n <- length(s)
  r <- 1:n
  hb <- alpha/(n - r + 1)
  x <- s < hb
  if(all(s < hb)) return(alpha) else
  m <- min(which(x == F))
  s[m]
}
